title: WEDNESDAY 5/26 - DAK IS BACK
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY 5/26 - DAK IS BACK
description:
Packers head coach Matt LaFleur (0:23) addresses the Aaron Rodgers situation. Falcons head coach Arthur Smith (1:02) does the same with Julio Jones...sort of. Bills QB Josh Allen (1:42) continues to work on his craft, while Bengals QB Joe Burrow (2:43) back on the field after his knee injury. Cowboys QB Dak Prescott (3:02) feeling good in Dallas, while Ryan Fitzpatrick (3:22) talks about his new team in Washington. Plus, Jimmy Garoppolo (3:59) talks about how he felt when the team drafted Trey Lance
